      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已创建子图O（ActuatorController），内部放置OUT节点。VFI到OUT标注\"spillover demand\"，DISC到OUT标注\"occupancy loop\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VFI",
